  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, You can bring yourself deeper into the heritage and teachings of the Hoshimi clan. You gain 1 of the following benefits;</p><ul><li><strong>Mastery of the Blade.</strong> You gain 1 rank of Mastery in 1 Melee Weapon you are proficient in.</li><li><strong>Mastery of the Hunt.</strong> You gain 1 rank of Mastery in the Survival, Investigation, and Perception skills. If you do not have proficiency in them, you instead gain proficiency.</li><li><strong>Mastery of the Frost.</strong> You gain a +2 bonus to Concentration checks and Clash checks made involving jutsu you cast with both the Water Release and Wind Release Keywords.</li></ul><p>You can choose an additional bonus at 18th level. You can choose the same bonus twice.</p>",
